  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, storm.trident.operation.EachOperation, storm.trident.operation.Operation, storm.trident.state.QueryFunction<AsyncHBaseState,com.stumbleupon.async.Deferred<java.util.ArrayList<org.hbase.async.KeyValue>>>

    public class AsyncHBaseStateQuery
extends storm.trident.state.BaseQueryFunction<AsyncHBaseState,com.stumbleupon.async.Deferred<java.util.ArrayList<org.hbase.async.KeyValue>>>
    This function is used to query an AsyncHBaseState with TridentStream.stateQuery(State, StateQuery,...)

    You have to provide some AsyncHBase fields mappers to map tuple fields to HBase RPC GetRequests.

    Even if the execute function in synchronous all RPCs for the batch will run in a parallel.

    Look at storm.asynchbase.example.topology.AsyncHBaseTridentStateExampleTopology for a concrete use case.
